Title: Multiresolution analysis by infinitely differentiable compactly supported functions  
Author: N. Dyn A. Ron 
Keyword: Key Words: up function, shift-invariant spaces, wavelets, multiresolution analysis, spectral approximation orders, stability.  
Address: Tel-Aviv, Israel Madison, Wisconsin 53706, USA  
